Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}『WOLF字幕組』      (www.wolfsub.com)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜留宿百姓家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人情意何其深
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀霜一縷飄閨裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海枯石爛誓願花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏僻鄉下武士還敢囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江戶改叫東京了？開玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世道 武士竟然不得不落草為寇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼改革
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你們看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從土佐來的岡田以藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯 去給我弄飯來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您請進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這女人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我拿著帶血的刀也面不改色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢 等天亮了就宰了她 拿了值錢的東西就走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是想在此留宿的話 請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏面還有一間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的閨房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久未整理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要向裏張望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論發生什麼事 都請切記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經…夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑…蜜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個頭是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人砍了你的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下落不明？ 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人 已經自己送上門來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必已經有心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這兒是…哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道又能怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己的名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人不知道自己的名字嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…我是弁慶…是弁慶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯了 你是九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 那是我家少爺的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好看看自己的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎啊 你為什麼會喜歡那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個吸取死人鮮血的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從第一眼看到那個女人開始 我就抑制不了對她的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著那個女人我感到自己的血在沸騰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了她我覺得自己什麼都能去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有個叫弁慶的侍從麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說那個奴才嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同與黑蜜相擁比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他一起旅行簡直就是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充其量只是個空有蠻力的蠢才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在再問你一次 你的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我麼 我的名字是九郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 名字是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 名字是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是！…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎加入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她…正在吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吸血的感覺竟然如此美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間的 盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界上 誰都不會追來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量也是受別人所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那遙遠的幾乎快要被忘記的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您把牙齒陷入我的脖子裏吸血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會成為不死之身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們的生命連為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還疼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 你就成了我的同類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也許我已經把你引上了一條不歸路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已經說了我不會因此後悔的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要為我擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是誰 吸血後剛開始都會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一會兒 只要堅持一會兒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吧 雖然說是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是疼痛的感覺和與常人無異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是我從古至今費盡無數日夜 尋找不死之秘的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天我已經等了多久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在這女人身體裏的不死的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把它連根挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,義經 你怎麼還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人 您還不能多走動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛開始止血的肩傷又要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和您的血還沒有徹底融合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的這力量到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是因為血的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的秘密是血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠喝下不死者的血來獲得永生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:19:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要喝下這女人的血我就能長生不老了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 九郎少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做夢也沒料到會發生這種事 所以一直去了平泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 追兵馬上又要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一刻都不能耽誤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道有能在天亮前偷偷下山的路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 應該有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不能見到你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不留神睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜 你在哪兒

